COMMS: FLASH TRAFFIC — COMSUBLANT TO USS BREMERTON.
COMMS: You are operating alone in the Barents Sea. No surface support. No air cover. Nearest friendly asset is four hundred miles south.
INTEL: Soviet Northern Fleet activity has increased significantly in the past seventy-two hours. Multiple surface groups and at least three submarine contacts in your operating area.
COMMS: Your mission: penetrate the patrol zone and collect acoustic intelligence on the new Akula-II variant. Intelligence believes one is conducting workups north of your position.
COMMS: Do not be detected. If compromised, break contact and withdraw south. Engagement is authorized only in self-defense.
COMMS: You are on your own. COMMS out.
